text: Itumbiara denudata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2005. It is known from Costa Rica.BioLib.cz - Itumbiara denudata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2005
title: Itumbiara denudata
